Title: Deformation Quantization of the Heisenberg Group
Authors: F.Bonechi, R.Giachetti, E.Sorace and M.Tarlini (Dipartimento di
  Fisica, Universita` di Firenze and INFN--Firenze, Dipartimento di Matematica,
  Universita` di Bologna.)
Comments: (TeX 9 pages, some misprints are here corrected)
Journal-ref: Commun.Math.Phys. 169 (1995) 627-634
\\
  A *-product compatible with the comultiplication of the Hopf algebra of the
functions on the Heisenberg group is determined by deforming a coboundary
Lie-Poisson structure defined by a classical r-matrix satisfying the modified
Yang-Baxter equation. The corresponding quantum group is studied and its
R-matrix is explicitly calculated.
